cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.FL, cs.SE, cs.CL 

This paper deals with inferring types for logic programs, which is a topic in programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses the use of constraints and regular types, which are topics in logic (cs.LO) and formal languages (cs.FL). Additionally, the paper proposes enhancements to the procedure for solving constraint systems, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and computational logic (cs.CL).
